{"tid":476017,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"千萬劏房盤加推25伙　一房都要1300萬","createTime":"2017-11-21T15:33:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-22T06:10:28.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b15ae1a943ac48cf3c13fd5286bdb7a16e34f432","tid":476017,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T15:33:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iEvzAf42TiE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DiEvzAf42TiE&d=oh0x7qK8nOqAef1Cr4y0bxxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=44b2069e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iEvzAf42TiE</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171121/20221013\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171121%2F20221013&d=oh0x7qK8nOqAef1Cr4y0bxxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=6792fe0a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171121%2F20221013&h=5a8028ed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171121/20221013</a><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】資助房屋群情洶湧，無非因發展商定價卻令人卻步，能負擔者少之又少。以港島區為例，新世界旗下西營盤劏房新盤瑧蓺，早前有221呎納米樓叫價過千萬，昨再提價最多半成加推25伙，當中最貴一房戶，實用面積僅347方呎，定價卻逾1,300萬元。<br />\n <img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20171121/large/a0206a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171121%2Flarge%2Fa0206a.gif&h=7be46fae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n實用面積347方呎<br />\n瑧蓺上周五推出首批50伙，高層J室221方呎問鼎全港最貴開放式劏房，定價過千萬元。新世界營業及市務高級總監楊文昨稱，瑧蓺新一批25伙屬於加價加推，提價幅度介乎0.5%至約半成。發展商今次制訂加推價單時明顯有所忌諱，25伙加推戶中有13伙屬開放式單位，較多位處中低層，最貴的高層C室定價約855.6萬元，扣盡發展商優惠，折實價約684.5萬元，呎價近3.1萬元。<br />\n新世界雖暫將瑧蓺高層開放式封印，但推出價格更驚人的一房單位。昨加推單位中的31樓G室，實用面積347方呎，定價1,302.7萬元，呎價3.75萬元，屬樓盤目前最貴一房戶，用盡發展商最高樓價兩成優惠，折實價仍逾1,042萬元，呎價逾3萬元。項目周五將發售65伙，予系內員工優先認購，繼而予購買最多5伙的大手客揀樓。市傳收票約140票，賬面超額認購約一倍。"},{"pid":"28eb6c8c1373eeaa91db60ac3b8f77954d17af56","tid":476017,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T16:02:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52a059d4454c46f67e84de99a13f505ab44beae4","tid":476017,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T17:17:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"731bdc7e7a6f2f82057efacf77d90a10fa779e91","tid":476017,"uid":609,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T23:55:43.000Z","msg":"港豬業主: 依家樓算平 只係年輕人唔努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c14d0d24e7b5c73c60498d7e79ba5a4fb524e159","tid":476017,"uid":38216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T00:04:48.000Z","msg":"佢心諗：我唔搵你啲傻仔笨，邊個會買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a28242d75494ee6ac97112fa400c32a2ab40648","tid":476017,"uid":52595,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T00:08:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5afad5042c0f103ca719d6deec2123064615dc3a","tid":476017,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T06:10:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}